         <body>
            <div type="recto">
               <figure>
                  <graphic url="19700920_0002r.png"/>
                  <figDesc>[Photographer holding camera, seated on pillar in front of the Parthenon
                     and looking away] </figDesc>
<head>Untitled</head>
              
 </figure>
            </div>
            <div type="verso" facs="19700920_0002v.png">

               <div type="message">
                  <p>Ios, Sep 20th </p>
                  <p>Dear Lou,</p>
                  <p> Enclosed, photo from Athens, as promised. Took half an hour to explain to the
                     old guy who took the picture what I wanted.</p>
                  <p> Ios OK, but knee-deep in hippies, so me + my camera set sail for ????
                     today.</p>
                  <salute> Rave on, Marco</salute>
               </div>
               <div type="destination">
                  <p><stamp type="postage">Four 0.5 dr. stamps, commemorating a priest, name
                        illegible.</stamp><stamp>Several postmarks, also
                     illegible.</stamp><address><addrLine>Mr Lou Burnard </addrLine><addrLine>Balliol College</addrLine><addrLine>Oxford, OXON</addrLine><addrLine> UK </addrLine><addrLine>ή Мεγάλη Βρεταννια</addrLine></address></p>
               </div>
            </div>
