      <text n="19740904_0006">
         <body>
            <div type="recto">
               <figure>
                  <graphic url="19740904_0006r.png"/>
                  <figDesc>[Monochrome view showing several seabirds in foreground, Cape Cornwall in
                     background]</figDesc>
              <head>Cape Cornwall, St Just in Penwith.<lb/> England's most westerly point
                     and only Cape.</head> </figure>
            </div>
            <div type="verso" facs="19740904_0006v.png">
               <div type="message">
                  <p>It seems rather silly to write to you from Oxford, so here you are. Come and
                     see us at Gotham sometime – any time, especially week-ends.</p>
                  <salute>Love from,<lb/> Christine</salute>
               </div>
               <div type="destination">
                  <p><stamp>REMEMBER to use the POST CODE!</stamp>
                     <stamp>Penzance – Cornwall <date when="1974-09-04T12:15">1215 PM. 4 Sep 1974</date></stamp>
                     <stamp  type="postage">Machin design. 4½p, pale blue.</stamp>
                     <address><addrLine>Lou and Lilette Burnard,</addrLine><addrLine>12 Harefields,</addrLine><addrLine>Summertown,</addrLine><addrLine>OXFORD</addrLine></address></p>
               </div>
            </div>
